t distribution is salary. Most people earn in the low/medium range of salaries, with a few exceptions (CEOs, professional athletes etc.) that are distributed along a large range (long “tail”) of higher values.","position":{"start":{"line":59,"column":1},"end":{"line":59,"column":1}},"key":"InEXsX9H4E"}],"key":"nUxhLAGPCd"},{"type":"heading","depth":2,"position":{"start":{"line":61,"column":1},"end":{"line":61,"column":1}},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"Skewed Left Distributions","position":{"start":{"line":61,"column":1},"end":{"line":61,"column":1}},"key":"GYigjIAJPk"}],"identifier":"skewed-left-distributions","label":"Skewed Left Distributions","html_id":"skewed-left-distributions","implicit":true,"key":"NMDFuCF1ET"},{"type":"container","kind":"figure","children":[{"type":"image","url":"/build/histogram6-8e577d0498d4ec6b2959c94fc666d399.gif","alt":"A Skewed-Left histogram. As we proceed from left to right across the x-axis, the bars rapidly slowly to the peak of the histogram, located at roughly x=78. From there, the values rapidly decrease, and the last measurement is at x=90. Since the X-axis starts at 0, the peak is offset to the right of the center of the histogram.","key":"wurpTM15y3","urlSource":"images/histogram6.gif"},{"type":"caption","children":[{"type":"paragraph","position":{"start":{"line":66,"column":1},"end":{"line":66,"column":1}},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"A Skewed-Left histogram. As we proceed from left to right across the x-axis, the bars rapidly slowly to the peak of the histogram, located at roughly x=78. From there, the values rapidly decrease, and the last measurement is at x=90. Since the X-axis starts at 0, the peak is offset to the right of the center of the histogram.","position":{"start":{"line":66,"column":1},"end":{"line":66,"column":1}},"key":"haqN75Nr28"}],"key":"SvLBd6qBxQ"}],"key":"bcDKKz3Nal"}],"enumerator":"6","key":"vdzEBAxI2U"},{"type":"paragraph","position":{"start":{"line":69,"column":1},"end":{"line":69,"colum